{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602740/extras/marketing_headings-01.png?t=1740350261\" />You wake up, somewhere deep in space, with no knowledge of your whereabouts... Who are you, and where did you come from? Who are the strange creatures living in this realm? A long road of discovery lies ahead, and secrets are hidden everywhere across this vast world... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602740/extras/holu.gif?t=1740350261\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602740/extras/marketing_headings-02.png?t=1740350261\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To progress, you must learn to harness the natural forces of the universe. Gravity, wind, magnetic fields and other features of the environment will guide your every move. Planets are guarded by cryptic puzzles that you'll need to decode, and unique challenges await you at every turn. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602740/extras/ship.gif?t=1740350261\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602740/extras/marketing_headings-03.png?t=1740350261\" />Experience rich and immersive planetary environments. Waves of heat rising from the sun-baked rock, rumbles of thunder deep inside a gas giant planet, water trickling through an alien swamp... Feel yourself transported to a wild world lightyears from Earth. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602740/extras/marketing_headings-04.png?t=1740350261\" />Solaro's vast world and soundtrack were created by a single developer over several years. Every fragment of the game has been crafted by hand to create a totally unique and original experience. Solaro was built from the open-source game engine Libgdx.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602740/extras/marketing_headings-05.png?t=1740350261\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">50+ vibrant alien worlds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">40+ unique &quot;orbital puzzles&quot;</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">12+ hours of core gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">12+ hours of optional features</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">100+ collectibles and achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">2.5 hours of original music </p></li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1602740?t=1740350261","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602740/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1740350261","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602740/18907cb46c8abdf51627187cc26820573924cadb/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740350261","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602740/18907cb46c8abdf51627187cc26820573924cadb/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1740350261","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2801690,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1602740/extras/mar